definition.en:
The date and time at which the object was updated.
see [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated)
definition.de:
Das Datum und die Uhrzeit, zu der das Objekt aktualisiert wurde.
siehe [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated)
definition.fr:
La date et l'heure auxquelles l'objet a été mis à jour.
voir [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated)
definition.es:
La fecha y hora en que se actualizó el objeto.
ver [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-updated)

example.en:
[Example 137](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#ex158-jsonld)

 ```json 
{
  "@context": "https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams",
  "name": "Cranberry Sauce Idea",
  "type": "Note",
  "content": "Mush it up so it does not have the same shape as the can.",
  "updated": "2014-12-12T12:12:12Z"
}
```
